Class GameState

java.lang.Object
game.GameState
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable
public class GameState extends Object implements Serializable, Cloneable
This class is where all the variables concerning game state are stored. This class alone is sufficient to recreate the game from scratch.
